-x-twitter-after-deepfake-uproar-3578414">暂时阻止了斯威夫特的名字被搜索</a>。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/tv/the-west-wing-solves-how-taylor-swift-can-make-it-super-bowl-3579249">《白宫风云》一文解答了泰勒·斯威夫特如何跻身超级碗的难题，该帖子</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">《NME》</a>上。</p> ;
